## Tailwind Best Practices

- Use `cn()` from `lib/utils.ts` for conditional classes (comes with shadcn/ui setup)
- Avoid arbitrary values `[...]` unless strictly necessary
- Keep responsive prefixes consistent: `sm:` ŌåÆ `md:` ŌåÆ `lg:`
- Dark mode: use `dark:` variants if needed, configure in `tailwind.config.ts`

