## Performance Checklist

- [ ] Images use `next/image` with explicit `width` and `height`
- [ ] Dynamic imports for heavy components: `const Chart = dynamic(() => import('./Chart'), { ssr: false })`
- [ ] `generateStaticParams` for dynamic routes that can be pre-rendered
- [ ] No unnecessary `'use client'` directives
- [ ] API routes validate input with zod before processing

---

## Quick Anti-Patterns to Avoid

| ŌØī Avoid | Ō£ģ Do instead |
|---------|-------------|
| `pages/` directory | `app/` directory |
| `<img>` tags | `<Image>` from next/image |
| Hardcoded secrets | `.env.local` + `.env.example` |
| `.js` / `.jsx` files | `.ts` / `.tsx` files |
| `any` type | Proper types or `unknown` |
| Inline styles | Tailwind classes |
| `useEffect` for data fetching | Server Components or SWR |
| Custom CSS files | Tailwind utilities |
| `console.log` in production code | Remove or use proper logger |

---

## Before Writing Code ŌĆō Checklist

1. Is this a Server or Client Component? Default to Server.
2. Does it need env vars? ŌåÆ Add to `.env.example`
3. Is there user input? ŌåÆ Validate with zod
4. Are there images? ŌåÆ Use `next/image`
5. Is there a loading state? ŌåÆ Add `loading.tsx`
6. Will this be in GitHub? ŌåÆ No secrets, clean `.gitignore`
